----------------------
planning for books app
----------------------

1. create web server.
2. setup model / controller / view / route.
   - model : bookModel
   - controller : bookController
   - view : books folder
   - routes : bookRoutes.
     - GET all books : /books
     - GET single book : /books/title
     - POST add book : /books
     - GET to create new book : books/create
     - GET to update single book : /books/id/edit
     - UPDATE single book : /books/id
     - DELETE single book : /books/id/delete